## Available Subagents

| Subagent | Primary Use |
|---|---|
| equity-price | Current market price (MANDATORY), historical market cap for 5-year own-multiples computation |
| equity-estimates | Forward EPS, EBITDA, P/E — NTM metrics for multiples valuation; analyst price target consensus |
| etf-index | Market-level P/E and EV/EBITDA benchmarks (index_sp500_multiples, etf_sectors) |
| discovery-screening | Peer EV/EBITDA and P/E multiples (equity_compare_peers, equity_compare_groups) |
