- `upside_bull` — % upside to bull DCF NAV; null if current_price unavailable
- `downside_bear` — % change to bear DCF NAV (typically negative); null if current_price unavailable
- `risk_reward_ratio` — |upside_base / downside_bear|; null if downside_bear is zero or null
