- `key_valuation_drivers` — 3-5 specific, quantified driver statements
- `confidence` — 0.0–1.0; start at 1.0 and reduce by ~0.15 if equity-price quote unavailable, ~0.15 if forecast FCFs all null, ~0.10 per missing primary multiple source (no peer data, no estimates)
- `data_sources` — one entry per subagent: name, what was retrieved, period covered
- `limitations` — data gaps or assumption caveats (e.g. "Historical own-multiples unavailable — 5-year EV/EBITDA comparison omitted", "Beta unavailable — WACC computed with beta=1.0 assumption")
